               <msContents>
                  <summary> Seventh volume an incomplete set of the <title>Rawz̤at al-Ṣafā</title>
                     (Garden of Purity), a general history from the creation of the world to the
                     time of the author, together with <ref
                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6656"><idno>Persian MS
                           173</idno></ref>, <ref
                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_14609"
                           ><idno>174</idno></ref>, <ref
                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_14610">175</ref>, <ref
                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6657">176</ref>, and
                        <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6659">178</ref>.
                     However, the set lacks the fourth volume and a geographical appendix often
                     added as the eighth, hence only six total. While most of the set appears nearly
                     uniformly bound, this volume completely differs from the others both in terms
                     of its text format and binding.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="manuscript_14610-item1">
                     <author key="person_175393012" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/175393012/"
                        change="#ids-cleanup">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Mīr Khvānd, Muḥammad ibn
                           Khāvandshāh, 1433-1498</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">مير خواند، محمد بن خواندشاه</persName>
                     </author>
                     <editor role="scr"><persName key="person_f6589">Muḥammad ‘Alī ibn Muḥammad
                        Shafī‘</persName></editor>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_273" change="#ids-cleanup">Rawz̤at
                        al-Ṣafā fī Sīrat al-Anbiyā wa-al-Mulūk</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt" key="work_273">Rawz̤at
                        al-Ṣafā</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_273" change="#ids-cleanup">روضة الصفاء فی سیرة
                        الانبيا و الملوك</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar" type="basmallah"><locus from="1b" to="1b"> برگ ۱پ (folio
                           1b):</locus> حصول سعادت دارین حمد پرورد کاریست... </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa">
                        <locus from="183a" to="183a"> برگ ۱۸۳ر (folio 183a): </locus>سیر فلک باد
                        بگامش مدام * نامه امید بنامش تمام</explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="fa">
                        <locus from="183a" to="183a"> برگ ۱۸۳ر (folio 183a):</locus> تمام شد روضة
                        الصفا بتاریخ چهارم شهر ذی القعد[ة] یوم پنجشنبه وقت عصر سنه ۱۲۲۳ من هجرة
                        النبی صلی الله علیه و سلم بید احقر العباد محمدعلی ولد مرحوم محمد شفیع ساکن </colophon>
                     <colophon>Completed in the evening on <date calendar="#Hijri_qamari"
                           when="1808-12-22">4 Ẕī-al-Qa‘dah, 1223 AH (22 Dec. 1808 CE)</date> by
                           <persName role="scr">Muḥammad ‘Alī ibn Muḥammad
                        Shafī‘</persName>.</colophon>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
